  schema:name "The Ontology of Work Operations" ;
  schema:description "Work operations are the foundational ontology applied to work — tasks are things, plans are containers, status is state, assignments are acts. The same modeling problem that MUDs solve for fantasy worlds, operational systems solve for organizational work." ;
